{
  "stem": "18626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto, we were from August 15 [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] until July the 13th, 1944.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From 1941, August the 15th, till-- until July the 13th.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1944, they start to liquidate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Soviet army start to get closer and closer, chasing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans start to lose the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- start to retreat from all-- from all over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From Russia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Since Stalingrad, you know, they start to go all the way down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The last couple of years, we knew it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got information, you know, from some Lithuanians who had, you know, the special radios.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some Jewish people work for Lithuanians who were Lithuanians and Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were like Volksdeutsch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They lived in Lithuania, but-- but they were Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to call themself Volksdeutsch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one German, a Volksdeutsch, his name was Genske.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had a brigade of Jewish worker working for him in his machine shop outside of the ghetto, because he was working for the German army.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was wearing the brown, you know, band with the swastika, and he had a license to take out like 20 Jews to work for his shop.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a Volksdeutsch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A matter of fact, my father knew him very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That Genske.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that Genske gave all the time the news secretly to a couple of the men who worked for him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Genske knew how the war goes, where the losses are, where the second front is, and America entered the-- the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because we really didn't know the big war between the United States and Japan.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We really didn't know too much about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't know-- we knew when-- when the-- when the United States enter the war direct with Germany, but not too much.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
